phrases: I-I-I have a... fiancee?

Well, the thing is...

All right!

Another transfer student?

Okay.
Hello everybody, nice to meet you.

Die, Ichijo!

Oh, my...

Um, did you hear a word that I said?

A date?
Not happening!
Not happening!

Remember?

Say ah!

In that case...

Oh?

But!
If only you would remember me, Raku-sama, then I am sure...

So why do you like me so much, anyway?
I do not remember if I ever did anything that would make you like me this much.
That is the part that I really do not get.
So you done forgot even that, huh?

So you done forgot even that, huh?

Rakkun, you...

Finally!
Rakkun...

No way!
Mari?
